data.description: Welcome to this breathtaking 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in the gated Vinehaven Addition in West-Moore.  This beauty has been loved from head to toe with brand new Anderson windows and doors, new roof & gutters, new interior & exterior paint, new contemporary lighting, plantation shutters in bedrooms, etc.  Enjoy high ceilings, and totally split floor plan with lovely natural light.  The primary suite is so spacious with private back patio access, gas fireplace with new blower, loaded primary bath with jetted tub, and large walk-in closet.  Secondary bedrooms are just a roomy and share a jack & jill style bathroom.  The living room is huge and shares a two way gas log fireplace with the dining area in the kitchen.  Beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, island, breakfast bar, and tons of storage.  Outdoor space is just as functional with large covered patio, wood burning fireplace, and plenty of space for entertaining.  3-car tandem garage with comfortable stairway access to attic that provides tons of storage. There's too much to list and so much to see, so schedule your private showing soon!
